\c 283 
\pc \bd NONE N’IGIHE C’UBUNTU\bd*
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd None n’igihe c’ubuntu, kubwawe mu nyavyaha, nufate uyu mwanya ng’uze ku Mukiza. Ku musozi Kalvari, yafash’ ivyaha vyawe, ngwino kuri We mugenzi, kugira akubuhore.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ubuntu butovugwa, bwuguruye ijuru, ngo buhe uwatsindwa umunezero uhoraho. Ngwino ubu mwaka kanya kw’uwo Musaraba, w’Iyo Ncuti ihebuje Yesu Mwami w’abami.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Umwansi agerageje, oh ntiwumvirize ijwi ryiwe rihenda. Wanke ivyo akuzanira, wegere ushize amanga, wihereze Umukiza, uzobona ububasha bwiwe buguhindura.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ubuntu butovugwa, bwuguruye ijuru, ngo buhe uwatsindwa umunezero uhoraho. Ngwino ubu mwaka kanya kw’uwo Musaraba, w’Iyo Ncuti ihebuje Yesu Mwami w’abami.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Yesu We arakwishuza, araguhamagara, ngo akize ubugingo bwawe kuj’ikuzimu. Ngw’ahindure ubugorwa, ahanagure ivyaha, ngo Agushiremwo umuco, wabo Yacunguye.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ubuntu butovugwa, bwuguruye ijuru, ngo buhe uwatsindwa umunezero uhoraho. Ngwino ubu mwaka kanya kw’uwo Musaraba, w’Iyo Ncuti ihebuje Yesu Mwami w’abami.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ubu buzima ni buto, ntawuzi ko ejo atazofata inzira atakigaruka. Imbere yuko biba ng’ube wacerewe, fata Agakiza atanga, Yesu abe uwawe.\bd*
